{"tid":314202,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【一周必看】遇著另類「健身教練」租客　林伯豪宅變SM淫窟","createTime":"2017-07-09T03:30:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-09T09:18:18.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a0949662ca0fc7026aad770383dce8cce1fdec57","tid":314202,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T03:30:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20083677&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170709\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20083677%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170709&d=Cv9dvMquDalcFwiy0o%2FDREbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=d58fba69\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20083677%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170709&h=6b28cedb\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20083677&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170709</a><br />\n<br />\n【一周必看】<br />\n遇著另類「健身教練」租客　林伯豪宅變SM淫窟<br />\n<br />\n港聞&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n有樓收租相信係唔少人嘅夢想，不過，係揀租客上就要好小心，如果唔係，隨時可能好似已退休英格蘭中場林柏特咁。據英國《太陽報》報道，「林伯」將佢喺倫敦嘅價值200萬鎊豪宅租咗畀一名自己係健身教練嘅37歲女子達雲娜。點知，原來達雲娜係「另類健身教練」，佢嘅服務包括喺屋入面同客人玩SM，將客人綁起及鞭打佢哋，每小時收費400鎊，額外畀多100鎊，仲可以拍埋片㖭！達雲娜暗示，只要客人出得起錢，佢仲可以提供埋可卡因畀佢哋。<br />\n<br />\n據「林伯」嘅朋友話，39歲嘅「林伯」對事件並唔知情，家陣知道後，佢會立即處理喎。"},{"pid":"2ea2388d48192c62e01b12b5aa87a6ac2940edf0","tid":314202,"uid":11809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T03:35:02.000Z","msg":"幫襯埋啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1603091996862363f434b46f6f295c280481e23a","tid":314202,"uid":14719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T05:15:52.000Z","msg":"ssp yoyo"},{"pid":"91d1edb2468ed82aa4809fa84bcc46278e0c4bfe","tid":